{"tid":592893,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家同啲有障礙嘅人有過咩難忘經驗","createTime":"2018-03-14T14:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T04:18:37.000Z","uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c762b9e08d4ab529ac3a7bf6c01816cdaeb553b3","tid":592893,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"話說今日同班fd出街<br />\n成班去廁所個陣見到有條分叉路行去育嬰室<br />\n就諗住行過去試下間嘢個自動鎖<br />\n點知有個懷仔size咁差唔多樣嘅男仔喺我哋後面提我哋<br />\n&quot;廁所喺嗰邊呀&quot;<br />\n個時就聽佢講去返佢指嗰個方向<br />\n係廁格我哋屙緊尿個陣<br />\n懷仔無啦啦喺我左邊申個頭裝我碌撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個下呆咗唔識比反應<br />\n同佢講<br />\n&quot;喂個到唔睇得㗎！&quot;<br />\n我個fd係隔離望到呆咗&mdash;&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事後佢話如果係佢應該就一下肘落去 <br />\n不過佢懷仔咁款佢發難我真係淆哂底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f8469cf8c0e0e855220f8338df34bc18d6acdd","tid":592893,"uid":65408,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:47:03.000Z","msg":"無端端會對育嬰室嘅門鎖有興趣，我覺得懷仔比你更正常喎"},{"pid":"6ce4edae03d32447668d0615f82d848f73ac8589","tid":592893,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36f8469cf8c0e0e855220f8338df34bc18d6acdd","tid":592893,"uid":65408,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:47:03.000Z","msg":"無端端會對育嬰室嘅門鎖有興趣，我覺得懷仔比你更正常喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:11:17.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858bdc9b8acee1355d5030703331c1d22a27ce40","tid":592893,"uid":12842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:18:37.000Z","msg":"係廁格我哋屙緊尿個陣<br />\n 懷仔無啦啦喺我左邊申個頭裝我碌撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你同懷仔用一齊入同一格廁格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im